Name: Horny Alice: Gothic Run
About the game: Horny Alice: Gothic Run is a colorful runner with a Gothic setting in which you play as the beautiful girl. Run as far as possible avoiding various obstacles such as tentacles or gargoyles. Collect magic crystals to restore pleasant memories of the events associated with Alice. Once in a fairy kingdom, which did not know disasters, an evil force appeared. The main character's home village was cursed. And she will have to run away from her home. Admire gorgeous stylized village backgrounds. Enjoy a great soundtrack. Pick up different power-ups. Collect memory crystals to open sex scenes with Alice.
